msgid "0.05"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:137
msgid "同じCalculatorオブジェクトで複数のDFT計算を行う場合（MDなど）、セル変形の指標がこの値より大きければFFTグリッドを再定義します。"
msgstr ""
"When performing multiple DFT calculations with the same Calculator object"
" (e.g., MD), the FFT grid is redefined if the cell deformation metric is "
"greater than this value."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:139
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"変形の指標は、初回または前回更新時のセル行列を :math:`A_\\mathrm{old}` 、現在のセル行列を "
":math:`A_\\mathrm{new}` として :math:`A_\\mathrm{new}A_\\mathrm{old}^{-1} - "
"I` の全成分の2乗和の平方根です。"
msgstr ""
"The deformation metric is the square root of the sum of squares of all "
"components of :math:`A_\\mathrm{new}A_\\mathrm{old}^{-1} - I` , where "
":math:`A_\\mathrm{old}` is the cell matrix at the initial or previous "
"update and :math:`A_\\mathrm{new}` is the current cell matrix."

