"PyTorchのOpenMP(CPU)スレッド並列数です。Noneの場合、環境変数 :envvar:`OMP_NUM_THREADS` "
"の値を使います。"
msgstr ""
"Number of OpenMP (CPU) threads for PyTorch. If None, the value of the "
"environment variable :envvar:`OMP_NUM_THREADS` is used."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:160
msgid "AtomicData関連"
msgstr "AtomicData related"

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:165
msgid "0.0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:167
msgid "系の正味の電荷です。系が全体としてイオン化している場合に設定します。"
msgstr "Net charge of the system. Set this if the system is ionized as a whole."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:171
msgid "float|None"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:174
msgid "系の正味のスピン偏極です。スピンあり(collinear)の計算で、スピン偏極を固定する場合に指定します。Noneを指定すると固定しません。"
msgstr ""
"Net spin polarization of the system. Specify this to fix the spin "
"polarization in spin-polarized (collinear) calculations. If set to None, "
"it is not fixed."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:179
msgid "60.0 / Bohr"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:181
msgid "逆空間の動径グリッドの最大値(1/Angstrom)の設定です。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for the maximum value of the radial grid in reciprocal space "
"(1/Angstrom)."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:186
#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:193
msgid "1001"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:188
msgid "逆空間の動径グリッドのグリッド数の設定です。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for the number of grid points of the radial grid in reciprocal "
"space."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:195
msgid "実空間の動径グリッドのグリッド数の設定です。"
msgstr "Setting for the number of grid points of the radial grid in real space."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:202
msgid ""
":math:`j`\\ 依存型擬ポテンシャルのプロジェクターを、\\ :math:`j`\\ "
"の縮退度を重みとして平均化することで、半相対論的（スカラー相対論的）擬ポテンシャルに変換するかどうかの設定です。False（DFT+U、スピン軌道相互作用）は未実装です。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for whether to convert :math:`j`\\ -dependent pseudopotential "
"projectors into semi-relativistic (scalar-relativistic) pseudopotentials "
"by averaging them using the degeneracy of :math:`j` as weights. False "
"(DFT+U, spin-orbit coupling) is not implemented."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:207
msgid "DFT関連"
msgstr "DFT related"

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:212 ../../usage/calculator.rst:53
msgid "non-polarized"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:214
msgid ""
"スピンを考慮した計算を行うかどうかの設定です。Noneまたは\"non-"
"polarized\"でスピン偏極なし、\"polarized\"でスピン偏極あり(collinear)、\"non-"
"collinear\"（未実装）でノンコリニア(非共線的)磁性の計算を行います。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for whether to perform calculations considering spin. Specify "
"None or \"non-polarized\" for non-spin-polarized, \"polarized\" for spin-"
"polarized (collinear), and \"non-collinear\" (not implemented) for non-"
"collinear magnetic calculations."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:218
msgid "int|tuple[int]|list[int]|torch.Tensor[int]"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:219
msgid "e_cutを元に設定"
msgstr "Set based on e_cut"

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:221
msgid ""
"電子密度のグリッド数の設定です。a、b、c方向のグリッド数を[na, nb, "
"nc]のように指定します。intの場合各方向に同じグリッド数を設定します。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for the number of grid points for the charge density. Specify the"
" number of grid points in the a, b, and c directions as [na, nb, nc]. If "
"an int is provided, the same number of grid points is set for each "
"direction."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:226 ../../usage/calculator.rst:59
msgid "75.0 * Hartree"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:228 ../../usage/calculator.rst:61
msgid "電子密度のカットオフエネルギー(eV)です。"
msgstr "Cutoff energy for the charge density (eV)."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:233
msgid "PBE"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:235
msgid "交換相関汎関数の種類です。\"LDA\"、\"PBE\"が指定できます。"
msgstr ""
"Type of exchange-correlation functional. \"LDA\" and \"PBE\" can be "
"specified."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:242
msgid "交換相関汎関数の計算で部分内殻補正(Partial Core Correction, PCC)を使うかどうかの設定です。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for whether to use Partial Core Correction (PCC) in the "
"calculation of the exchange-correlation functional."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:247 ../../usage/calculator.rst:29
msgid "AS25"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:249
msgid ""
"運動エネルギー汎関数を指定します。\"AS25\"でAdvanceSoft25汎関数を使用します。従来の汎関数として\"TFvW"
"\"(Thomas-Fermi-von Weizsäcker)、\"LKT\"(Luo-Karasiev-Trickey)が使えます。"
msgstr ""
"Specifies the kinetic energy functional. Specify \"AS25\" to use the "
"AdvanceSoft25 functional. \"TFvW\" (Thomas-Fermi-von Weizsäcker) and "
"\"LKT\" (Luo-Karasiev-Trickey) are available as conventional functionals."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:251
msgid "TFvWを使う場合、TFに対するvWの割合を\"TF1/5vW\"、\"TF0.8vW\"のように指定できます。割合を指定せず、かつkin_coef_tf、kin_coef_vwを指定しない場合は\"TF1/5vW\"となります。\"TF\"、\"vW\"のみも指定できます。"
msgstr ""
"When using TFvW, you can specify the ratio of vW to TF like \"TF1/5vW\" "
"or \"TF0.8vW\". If the ratio is not specified and neither kin_coef_tf nor"
" kin_coef_vw are specified, it defaults to \"TF1/5vW\". You can also "
"specify just \"TF\" or \"vW\"."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:256 ../../usage/calculator.rst:35
msgid "AdvanceSoft25-80Ry-ft"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:258
msgid ""
"AdvanceSoft25汎関数を使う場合、そのモデルを指定します。学習済みモデルは "
":file:`aofdft/deepkin/pretrained` にあります。学習済みモデルはファイル名のみ（拡張子なし）で指定できます。"
msgstr ""
"Specifies the model when using the AdvanceSoft25 functional. Pretrained "
"models are located in :file:`aofdft/deepkin/pretrained` . Pretrained "
"models can be specified by file name only (without extension)."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:263
#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:277
msgid "1.0"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:265
msgid "TFvW汎関数を使う場合のTFの係数です。"
msgstr "Coefficient for TF when using the TFvW functional."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:270
#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:331
msgid "0.2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:272
msgid "TFvW汎関数を使う場合のvWの係数です。"
msgstr "Coefficient for vW when using the TFvW functional."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:279
msgid "運動エネルギー汎関数に適用するスケーリング係数です。"
msgstr "Scaling coefficient applied to the kinetic energy functional."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:284
msgid "gauss"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:286
msgid ""
"Smearingの方法を設定します。\"gauss\"(ガウス関数)、\"m-p\"(Methfessel-Paxton)、\"m-v"
"\"(Marzari-Vanderbilt)、\"fermi\"(Fermi-Dirac)が指定できます。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for the smearing method. \"gauss\" (Gaussian function), \"m-p\" "
"(Methfessel-Paxton), \"m-v\" (Marzari-Vanderbilt), and \"fermi\" (Fermi-"
"Dirac) can be specified."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:291
msgid "0.02 * Hartree"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:293
msgid "Smearingの幅(eV)です。"
msgstr "Width of smearing (eV)."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:298
msgid "SCF関連"
msgstr "SCF related"

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:303
msgid "500"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:305
msgid "繰り返し回数の最大値です。"
msgstr "Maximum number of iterations."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:310
msgid "1.0e-6 * Hartree"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:312
msgid "エネルギーの収束条件の閾値(eV)です。"
msgstr "Threshold for the energy convergence condition (eV)."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:317
msgid "atomic"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:319
msgid "電子密度の初期値を与える方法を設定します。\"atomic\"（孤立原子の電子密度の重ね合わせ）、\"qeq\"（未実装）、\"density_matrix\"（既存の密度行列）が指定できます。初期値としてrhoを与える場合はNoneを指定できます。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for the method to provide the initial charge density. \"atomic\" "
"(superposition of isolated atom charge densities), \"qeq\" (not "
"implemented), and \"density_matrix\" (existing density matrix) can be "
"specified. You can also specify None if providing rho as the initial "
"value."

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:324
msgid "pulay"
msgstr ""

#: ../../usage/aodftcalculator_class.rst:326
msgid "電子密度を更新するときの混合法の設定です。\"simple\"（単純な線形混合）、\"pulay\"が指定できます。"
