"vectors), or \"SemiLocal\" (Machine learning model using semi-local "
"feature vectors)."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:17
msgid "特徴ベクトルの値の範囲を制限する活性化関数の設定です。\"null\"（適用しない）、\"fixed\"（固定重み付きtanh関数）、\"learnable\"（可変重み付きtanh関数）から指定します。"
msgstr ""
"Settings for the activation function to limit the range of feature vector"
" values. Specify from \"null\" (do not apply), \"fixed\" (fixed weighted "
"tanh function), or \"learnable\" (learnable weighted tanh function)."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:21
msgid "重み付きtanh関数の重みの初期値です。features_tanh=fixedの場合はこの値で固定されます。"
msgstr ""
"Initial value of the weight for the weighted tanh function. If "
"features_tanh=fixed, it is fixed at this value."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:25
msgid "重み付きtanh関数の重みの最小値です。"
msgstr "Minimum value of the weight for the weighted tanh function."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:29
msgid "重み付きtanh関数の重みの最大値です。"
msgstr "Maximum value of the weight for the weighted tanh function."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:33
msgid "特徴ベクトルとして電子密度の勾配とラプラシアンの2つを使う(False)か、勾配とラプラシアンの積を加えた3つを使う(True)かの設定です。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for whether to use two feature vectors: the gradient and "
"Laplacian of the charge density (False), or three feature vectors by "
"adding the product of the gradient and Laplacian (True)."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:37
msgid "隣接相関のカットオフ半径(Bohr)です。"
msgstr "Cutoff radius for adjacency correlation (Bohr)."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:41
msgid ""
"特徴ベクトルに対し隣接相関による畳み込み積分を行うときに、半径 :math:`R_i` ・幅 :math:`\\kappa_i` "
"の異なる複数の積分核（重み関数）を使います。 :math:`i` に対し :math:`R_i` "
"を等間隔に配置する(False)か、等比数列的に間隔を広げながら配置する(True)かの設定です。"
msgstr ""
"When performing convolution integrals using adjacency correlations on "
"feature vectors, multiple integral kernels (weight functions) with "
"different radii :math:`R_i` and widths :math:`\\kappa_i` are used. This "
"setting specifies whether to arrange :math:`R_i` at equal intervals with "
"respect to :math:`i` (False) or to arrange them with geometrically "
"increasing intervals (True)."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:45
msgid "long_tailed=Trueの場合に使うスケーリングパラメータです。"
msgstr "Scaling parameter used when long_tailed=True."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:49
msgid "積分核（重み関数）の数です。"
msgstr "The number of integral kernels (weight functions)."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:53
msgid "相互作用ブロック（畳み込み→多層パーセプトロンによる相互作用）の数です。"
msgstr ""
"The number of interaction blocks (interaction via convolution -> multi-"
"layer perceptron)."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:57
msgid "相互作用ブロックの多層パーセプトロンの隠れ層の次元数です。"
msgstr ""
"The number of dimensions of the hidden layer of the multi-layer "
"perceptron in the interaction block."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:61
msgid "相互作用ブロックの多層パーセプトロンの隠れ層の数です。"
msgstr ""
"The number of hidden layers of the multi-layer perceptron in the "
"interaction block."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:65
msgid "相互作用ブロックの多層パーセプトロンにGated Linear Unit(GLU)を使うかどうかの設定です。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for whether to use Gated Linear Unit (GLU) for the multi-layer "
"perceptron in the interaction block."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:69
msgid "相互作用ブロックの多層パーセプトロンでレイヤー正規化を使うかどうかの設定です。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for whether to use layer normalization for the multi-layer "
"perceptron in the interaction block."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:73
msgid "相互作用ブロックの多層パーセプトロンで残差接続（入力を出力に加算する）を行うかどうかの設定です。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for whether to use residual connections (adding the input to the "
"output) in the multi-layer perceptron of the interaction block."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:77
msgid "出力ブロックの多層パーセプトロンの隠れ層の次元数です。"
msgstr ""
"The number of dimensions of the hidden layer of the multi-layer "
"perceptron in the output block."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:81
msgid "出力ブロックの多層パーセプトロンの隠れ層の層数です。"
msgstr ""
"The number of hidden layers of the multi-layer perceptron in the output "
"block."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:85
msgid "出力ブロックの多層パーセプトロンにGated Linear Unit(GLU)を使うかどうかの設定です。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for whether to use Gated Linear Unit (GLU) for the multi-layer "
"perceptron in the output block."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:89
msgid "出力ブロックの多層パーセプトロンでレイヤー正規化を使うかどうかの設定です。"
msgstr ""
"Setting for whether to use layer normalization for the multi-layer "
"perceptron in the output block."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:93
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"汎グラフの出力を使って運動エネルギー密度 :math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r})` を計算するとき、TFvWモデルに対する補強因子 "
":math:`F^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})` として使います。このときのvWモデルの使い方を指定します。"
msgstr ""
"When calculating the kinetic energy density :math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r})` "
"using the output of the universal graph, it is used as an enhancement "
"factor :math:`F^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})` for the TFvW model. "
"This specifies how the vW model is used in this case."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:95
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"使わない(null): :math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r}) = \\tau^\\mathrm{TF}(\\mathbf{r}) "
"F_\\mathrm{TF}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})`"
msgstr ""
"Not used (null): :math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r}) = "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{TF}(\\mathbf{r}) "
"F_\\mathrm{TF}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})`"

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:96
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"補強因子なしで使う(fixed): :math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r}) = "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{TF}(\\mathbf{r}) "
"F_\\mathrm{TF}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r}) + "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{vW}(\\mathbf{r})`"
msgstr ""
"Used without enhancement factor (fixed): :math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r}) = "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{TF}(\\mathbf{r}) "
"F_\\mathrm{TF}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r}) + "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{vW}(\\mathbf{r})`"

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:97
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"補強因子を適用して使う(learnable): :math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r}) = "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{TF}(\\mathbf{r}) "
"F_\\mathrm{TF}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r}) + "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{vW}(\\mathbf{r}) "
"F_\\mathrm{vW}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})`"
msgstr ""
"Used with enhancement factor (learnable): :math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r}) = "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{TF}(\\mathbf{r}) "
"F_\\mathrm{TF}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r}) + "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{vW}(\\mathbf{r}) "
"F_\\mathrm{vW}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})`"

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:98
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"補強因子を差分として適用して使う(learnable_delta): :math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r}) = "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{TF}(\\mathbf{r}) "
"F_\\mathrm{TF}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r}) + "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{vW}(\\mathbf{r}) \\left(1 + "
"F_\\mathrm{vW}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})\\right)`"
msgstr ""
"Used with enhancement factor as a delta (learnable_delta): "
":math:`\\tau(\\mathbf{r}) = \\tau^\\mathrm{TF}(\\mathbf{r}) "
"F_\\mathrm{TF}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r}) + "
"\\tau^\\mathrm{vW}(\\mathbf{r}) \\left(1 + "
"F_\\mathrm{vW}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})\\right)`"

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:102
msgid "汎グラフの出力に適用する活性化関数を指定します。"
msgstr "Specifies the activation function to apply to the output of the Graphical."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:104
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"enhance_scale>1の場合: :math:`\\alpha` = enhance_scale とするSloping Step関数 "
":math:`(\\alpha/2)\\lbrace(\\tanh((2x/\\alpha-1)^n))^{1/n}+1\\rbrace`"
msgstr ""
"When enhance_scale > 1: Sloping Step function with :math:`\\alpha` = "
"enhance_scale "
":math:`(\\alpha/2)\\lbrace(\\tanh((2x/\\alpha-1)^n))^{1/n}+1\\rbrace`"

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:105
msgid "それ以外の場合: Softplus関数 :math:`(1/\\beta)\\log(1+\\exp(\\beta x))`"
msgstr "Otherwise: Softplus function :math:`(1/\\beta)\\log(1+\\exp(\\beta x))`"

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:109
msgid "Sloping Step関数の指数 :math:`n` です。奇数である必要があります。"
msgstr ""
"The exponent :math:`n` of the Sloping Step function. It must be an odd "
"number."

#: ../../usage/model_yml.rst:113
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"TFモデルに対する補強因子 :math:`F_\\mathrm{TF}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})` "
"に自由電子ガスモデルに基づくペナルティ関数を適用します。"
msgstr ""
"Applies a penalty function based on the free electron gas model to the "
"enhancement factor "
":math:`F_\\mathrm{TF}^\\mathrm{NN}[\\rho](\\mathbf{r})` for the TF model."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:5
