#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:27
msgid "教師データを常にメモリ上に読み込んでおくかどうかの設定です。"
msgstr "Setting for whether to always keep the training data loaded in memory."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:31
msgid ""
"最適化を行う手法を設定します。\"Adam\"、\"AdamW\"、\"SGD\"（確率的最急降下法）、\"mSGD\"(Momentum "
"SGD)から指定します。"
msgstr ""
"Specifies the optimization method. Select from \"Adam\", \"AdamW\", "
"\"SGD\" (Stochastic Gradient Descent), or \"mSGD\" (Momentum SGD)."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:35
msgid "学習率スケジューラー（学習率を動的に調整する方法）を設定します。"
msgstr ""
"Specifies the learning rate scheduler (a method for dynamically adjusting"
" the learning rate)."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:37
msgid "null: 調整しない"
msgstr "null: Do not adjust"

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:38
msgid "StepLR: 一定ステップごとに :math:`\\times\\gamma`"
msgstr "StepLR: :math:`\\times\\gamma` at regular steps"

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:39
msgid "ExpLR: 毎ステップ  :math:`\\times\\gamma`"
msgstr "ExpLR: :math:`\\times\\gamma` at every step"

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:40
msgid "CosLR: コサインアニーリング"
msgstr "CosLR: Cosine annealing"

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:41
msgid "CosRestartLR1: コサインアニーリング＋一定間隔のウォームリスタート"
msgstr "CosRestartLR1: Cosine annealing with warm restarts at fixed intervals"

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:42
msgid "CosRestartLR2: コサインアニーリング＋等比数列的間隔のウォームリスタート"
msgstr "CosRestartLR2: Cosine annealing with warm restarts at geometric intervals"

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:43
#, python-brace-format
msgid "ReduceLR: 損失関数が改善しなくなったら :math:`\\times\\mathrm{factor}`"
msgstr ""
"ReduceLR: :math:`\\times\\mathrm{factor}` when the loss function stops "
