"new model during training."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:99
msgid "教師データの順番をシャッフルするかどうかの設定です。"
msgstr "Settings for whether to shuffle the order of the training data."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:103
msgid "PyTorchのDataLoaderのワーカープロセス数です。"
msgstr "The number of worker processes for the PyTorch DataLoader."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:107
msgid ""
"損失関数の設定です。\"MSERatio\"（相対的な平均二乗誤差）、\"MSERatioExt\"（MSERatioの "
":math:`dT/d\\rho` の評価を密度で重み付けしたもの）、\"MAEEnergy\"（エネルギー単位での平均絶対誤差）から指定します。"
msgstr ""
"Sets the loss function. Specify from \"MSERatio\" (relative mean squared "
"error), \"MSERatioExt\" (MSERatio with evaluation of :math:`dT/d\\rho` "
"weighted by density), or \"MAEEnergy\" (mean absolute error in energy "
"units)."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:111
msgid "バッチの平均の損失関数がこの値よりも大きい場合、そのバッチは除外し、学習に使いません。"
msgstr ""
"If the average loss function of a batch is greater than this value, that "
"batch is excluded and not used for training."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:115
msgid ""
"損失関数の計算に運動エネルギー :math:`T` を使う(True)か、運動エネルギー密度 :math:`\\tau` "
"を使う(False)かの設定です。"
msgstr ""
"Whether to use kinetic energy :math:`T`\\ (True) or kinetic energy "
"density :math:`\\tau`\\ (False) for calculating the loss function."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:119
msgid ""
"電子密度がこの値よりも小さい場合、その点の :math:`dT/d\\rho` "
"を損失関数の評価から除外します。正の場合は絶対密度、負の場合は相対密度を使います。"
msgstr ""
"If the charge density is smaller than this value, :math:`dT/d\\rho` at "
"that point is excluded from the loss function evaluation. Absolute "
"density is used for positive values, and relative density is used for "
"negative values."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:123
msgid "損失関数を計算するときの、運動エネルギー :math:`T` の損失の重みです。"
msgstr ""
"The weight of the kinetic energy :math:`T` loss when calculating the loss"
" function."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:127
msgid "loss_type=MAEEnergyで、自由電子ガス(FEG)の損失をエネルギーに換算するときの係数(Hartree)です。"
msgstr ""
"The coefficient (Hartree) used to convert the free electron gas (FEG) "
"loss into energy when loss_type=MAEEnergy."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:131
msgid "学習に使う教師データのフォルダパスです。"
msgstr "The folder path of the training data used for learning."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:135
msgid "テストに使う教師データのフォルダパスです。"
msgstr "The folder path of the training data used for testing."

#: ../../usage/train_yml.rst:139
